name: Victini
flavorText: This Pokémon brings victory. It is saidthat Trainers with Victini always win,regardless of the type of encounter.

name: Snivy
flavorText: It is very intelligent and calm.Being exposed to lots of sunlight makesits movements swifter.

name: Servine
flavorText: It moves along the ground as if sliding.Its swift movements befuddle its foes,and it then attacks with a vine whip.

name: Serperior
flavorText: It can stop its opponents’movements with just a glare. It takesin solar energy and boosts it internally.

name: Tepig
flavorText: It can deftly dodge its foe’s attackswhile shooting fireballs from its nose.It roasts berries before it eats them.

name: Pignite
flavorText: When its internal fire flares up, itsmovements grow sharper and faster.When in trouble, it emits smoke.

name: Emboar
flavorText: It can throw a fire punch by setting itsfists on fire with its fiery chin. It caresdeeply about its friends.

name: Oshawott
flavorText: It fights using the scalchop on itsstomach. In response to an attack,it retaliates immediately by slashing.

name: Dewott
flavorText: Strict training is how it learns itsflowing double-scalchop technique.

name: Samurott
flavorText: One swing of the sword incorporated inits armor can fell an opponent. A simpleglare from one of them quiets everybody.

name: Patrat
flavorText: Using food stored in cheek pouches,they can keep watch for days. They usetheir tails to communicate with others.

name: Watchog
flavorText: When they see an enemy, their tailsstand high, and they spit the seeds ofberries stored in their cheek pouches.

name: Lillipup
flavorText: It faces strong opponents with greatcourage. But, when at a disadvantage ina fight, this intelligent Pokémon flees.

name: Herdier
flavorText: It has black, cape-like fur that isvery hard and decreases the amountof damage it receives.

name: Stoutland
flavorText: It rescues people stranded byblizzards in the mountains. Itsshaggy fur shields it from the cold.

name: Purrloin
flavorText: They steal from people for fun, but theirvictims can’t help but forgive them.Their deceptively cute act is perfect.

name: Liepard
flavorText: These Pokémon vanish and appearunexpectedly. Many Trainers are drawnto their beautiful form and fur.

name: Pansage
flavorText: This Pokémon dwells deep in the forest.Eating a leaf from its head whisksweariness away as if by magic.

name: Simisage
flavorText: Ill tempered, it fights by swinging itsbarbed tail around wildly. The leafgrowing on its head is very bitter.

name: Pansear
flavorText: When it is angered, the temperatureof its head tuft reaches 600° F.It uses its tuft to roast berries.

name: Simisear
flavorText: It loves sweets because they becomeenergy for the fire burning insideits body.

name: Panpour
flavorText: The water stored inside the tuft onits head is full of nutrients. Plantsthat receive its water grow large.

name: Simipour
flavorText: The tuft on its head holds water. Whenthe level runs low, it replenishes thetuft by siphoning up water with its tail.

name: Munna
flavorText: Munna always float in the air. Peoplewhose dreams are eaten by themforget what the dreams had been about.

name: Musharna
flavorText: The mist emanating from their foreheadsis packed with the dreams of peopleand Pokémon.

name: Pidove
flavorText: Each follows its Trainer’s orders asbest it can, but they sometimes fail tounderstand complicated commands.

name: Tranquill
flavorText: It can return to its Trainer’s locationregardless of the distanceseparating them.

name: Unfezant
flavorText: Males swing their head plumage tothreaten opponents. The females’ flyingabilities surpass those of the males.

name: Blitzle
flavorText: When thunderclouds cover the sky, it will appear.It can catch lightning with its mane and storethe electricity.

name: Zebstrika
flavorText: They have lightning-like movements.When Zebstrika run at full speed,the sound of thunder reverberates.

name: Roggenrola
flavorText: Its ear is hexagonal in shape.Compressed underground,its body is as hard as steel.

name: Boldore
flavorText: When it overflows with power,the orange crystal on its body glows.It looks for underground water in caves.

name: Gigalith
flavorText: Compressing the energy from itsinternal core lets it fire off an attackcapable of blowing away a mountain.

name: Woobat
flavorText: Its habitat is dark forests and caves.It emits ultrasonic waves from itsnose to learn about its surroundings.

name: Swoobat
flavorText: It emits sound waves of variousfrequencies from its nose, includingsome powerful enough to destroy rocks.

name: Drilbur
flavorText: It can dig through the groundat a speed of 30 mph. It could givea car running aboveground a good race.

name: Excadrill
flavorText: It can help in tunnel construction.Its drill has evolved into steel strongenough to bore through iron plates.

name: Audino
flavorText: It touches others with the feelers onits ears, using the sound of theirheartbeats to tell how they are feeling.

name: Timburr
flavorText: It fights by swinging a piece of lumberaround. It is close to evolving when itcan handle the lumber without difficulty.

name: Gurdurr
flavorText: This Pokémon is so muscular and stronglybuilt that even a group of wrestlerscould not make it budge an inch.

name: Conkeldurr
flavorText: It is thought that Conkeldurr taughthumans how to make concrete morethan 2,000 years ago.

name: Tympole
flavorText: They warn others of danger byvibrating their cheeks to createa high-pitched sound.

name: Palpitoad
flavorText: When they vibrate the bumps on theirheads, they can make waves in wateror earthquake-like vibrations on land.

name: Seismitoad
flavorText: They shoot paralyzing liquid from theirhead bumps. They use vibration to hurttheir opponents.

name: Throh
flavorText: When it tightens its belt, it becomesstronger. Wild Throh use vines to weavetheir own belts.

name: Sawk
flavorText: The sound of Sawk punching bouldersand trees can be heard all the way fromthe mountains where they train.

name: Sewaddle
flavorText: Leavanny dress it in clothes they madefor it when it hatched. It hides its headin its hood while it is sleeping.

name: Swadloon
flavorText: Forests where Swadloon live have superbfoliage because the nutrients they makefrom fallen leaves nourish the plant life.

name: Leavanny
flavorText: Upon finding a small Pokémon, it weavesclothing for it from leaves, using thecutters on its arms and sticky silk.

name: Venipede
flavorText: Its bite injects a potent poison, enoughto paralyze large bird Pokémon that tryto prey on it.

name: Whirlipede
flavorText: Protected by a hard shell, it spinsits body like a wheel and crashesfuriously into its enemies.

name: Scolipede
flavorText: With quick movements, it chases downits foes, attacking relentlessly withits horns until it prevails.

name: Cottonee
flavorText: When attacked, it escapes by shootingcotton from its body. The cotton servesas a decoy to distract the attacker.

name: Whimsicott
flavorText: Like the wind, it can slip through anygap, no matter how small. It leavesballs of white fluff behind.

name: Petilil
flavorText: The leaves on its head are very bitter.Eating one of these leaves is knownto refresh a tired body.

name: Lilligant
flavorText: Even veteran Trainers face a challengein getting its beautiful flower to bloom.This Pokémon is popular with celebrities.

name: Basculin-red-striped
flavorText: Red and blue Basculin get along sopoorly, they’ll start fighting instantly.These Pokémon are very hostile.

name: Sandile
flavorText: They live buried in the sands of thedesert. The sun-warmed sands preventtheir body temperature from dropping.

name: Krokorok
flavorText: They live in groups of a few individuals.Protective membranes shield their eyesfrom sandstorms.

name: Krookodile
flavorText: They never allow prey to escape.Their jaws are so powerful, they cancrush the body of an automobile.

name: Darumaka
flavorText: When its internal fire is burning, itcannot calm down and it runs around.When the fire diminishes, it falls asleep.

name: Darmanitan-standard
flavorText: Its internal fire burns at 2,500° F,making enough power that it candestroy a dump truck with one punch.

name: Maractus
flavorText: It uses an up-tempo song and danceto drive away the bird Pokémon thatprey on its flower seeds.

name: Dwebble
flavorText: This Pokémon can easily melt holes inhard rocks with a liquid secreted fromits mouth.

name: Crustle
flavorText: Competing for territory, Crustlefight viciously. The one whose boulderis broken is the loser of the battle.

name: Scraggy
flavorText: Its skin has a rubbery elasticity, soit can reduce damage by defensivelypulling its skin up to its neck.

name: Scrafty
flavorText: Groups of them beat up anythingthat enters their territory. Each canspit acidic liquid from its mouth.

name: Sigilyph
flavorText: They never vary the route they fly,because their memories of guardingan ancient city remain steadfast.

name: Yamask
flavorText: Each of them carries a mask that usedto be its face when it was human.Sometimes they look at it and cry.

name: Cofagrigus
flavorText: It has been said that they swallow thosewho get too close and turn them intomummies. They like to eat gold nuggets.

name: Tirtouga
flavorText: Restored from a fossil, this Pokémoncan dive to depths beyond half a mile.

name: Carracosta
flavorText: They can live both in the ocean and onland. A slap from one of them is enoughto open a hole in the bottom of a tanker.

name: Archen
flavorText: Said to be an ancestor of bird Pokémon,they were unable to fly and moved aboutby hopping from one branch to another.

name: Archeops
flavorText: They are intelligent and will cooperateto catch prey. From the ground, theyuse a running start to take flight.

name: Trubbish
flavorText: Inhaling the gas they belch will makeyou sleep for a week. They preferunsanitary places.

name: Garbodor
flavorText: It clenches opponents with its left armand finishes them off with foul-smellingpoison gas belched from its mouth.

name: Zorua
flavorText: It changes into the forms of othersto surprise them. Apparently, itoften transforms into a silent child.

name: Zoroark
flavorText: Bonds between these Pokémon are verystrong. It protects the safety of itspack by tricking its opponents.

name: Minccino
flavorText: They greet one another by rubbing eachother with their tails, which are alwayskept well groomed and clean.

name: Cinccino
flavorText: Their white fur is coated in a special oilthat makes it easy for them todeflect attacks.

name: Gothita
flavorText: Their ribbonlike feelers increase theirpsychic power. They are always staringat something.

name: Gothorita
flavorText: They use hypnosis to control people andPokémon. Tales of Gothorita leadingpeople astray are told in every corner.

name: Gothitelle
flavorText: Starry skies thousands of light-yearsaway are visible in the space distortedby their intense psychic power.

name: Solosis
flavorText: They drive away attackers by unleashingpsychic power. They can use telepathyto talk with others.

name: Duosion
flavorText: Since they have two divided brains,at times they suddenly try to take twodifferent actions at once.

name: Reuniclus
flavorText: When Reuniclus shake hands, a networkforms between their brains, increasingtheir psychic power.

name: Ducklett
flavorText: These bird Pokémon are excellent divers.They swim around in the water eatingtheir favorite food--peat moss.

name: Swanna
flavorText: Swanna start to dance at dusk.The one dancing in the middle isthe leader of the flock.

name: Vanillite
flavorText: The temperature of their breathis -58° F. They create snow crystals andmake snow fall in the areas around them.

name: Vanillish
flavorText: Snowy mountains are this Pokémon’shabitat. During an ancient ice age, theymoved to southern areas.

name: Vanilluxe
flavorText: Swallowing large amounts of water, theymake snow clouds inside their bodies andattack their foes with violent blizzards.

name: Deerling
flavorText: The color and scent of their fur changesto match the mountain grass. When theysense hostility, they hide in the grass.

name: Sawsbuck
flavorText: They migrate according to the seasons.People can tell the season by looking atSawsbuck’s horns.

name: Emolga
flavorText: The energy made in its cheeks’ electricpouches is stored inside its membraneand released while it is gliding.

name: Karrablast
flavorText: These mysterious Pokémon evolve whenthey receive electrical stimulation whilethey are in the same place as Shelmet.

name: Escavalier
flavorText: They fly around at high speed, strikingwith their pointed spears. Even when introuble, they face opponents bravely.

name: Foongus
flavorText: It lures people in with its Poké Ballpattern, then releases poison spores.Why it resembles a Poké Ball is unknown.

name: Amoonguss
flavorText: It lures prey close by dancing andwaving its arm caps, which resemblePoké Balls, in a swaying motion.

name: Frillish
flavorText: With its thin, veil-like arms wrappedaround the body of its opponent,it sinks to the ocean floor.

name: Jellicent
flavorText: The fate of the ships and crew thatwander into Jellicent’s habitat:all sunken, all lost, all vanished.

name: Alomomola
flavorText: The special membrane envelopingAlomomola has the ability to heal wounds.

name: Joltik
flavorText: Joltik that live in cities have learneda technique for sucking electricityfrom the outlets in houses.

name: Galvantula
flavorText: When attacked, they create anelectric barrier by spitting outmany electrically charged threads.

name: Ferroseed
flavorText: When threatened, it attacks byshooting a barrage of spikes, which givesit a chance to escape by rolling away.

name: Ferrothorn
flavorText: It fights by swinging around its threespiky feelers. A hit from these steelspikes can reduce a boulder to rubble.

name: Klink
flavorText: The two minigears that mesh togetherare predetermined. Each will reboundfrom other minigears without meshing.

name: Klang
flavorText: By changing the direction in which itrotates, it communicates its feelings toothers. When angry, it rotates faster.

name: Klinklang
flavorText: The gear with the red core isrotated at high speed for arapid energy charge.

name: Tynamo
flavorText: While one alone doesn’t have much power,a chain of many Tynamo can be aspowerful as lightning.

name: Eelektrik
flavorText: They coil around foes and shock themwith electricity-generating organs thatseem simply to be circular patterns.

name: Eelektross
flavorText: They crawl out of the ocean using theirarms. They will attack prey on shore andimmediately drag it into the ocean.

name: Elgyem
flavorText: It uses its strong psychic powerto squeeze its opponent’s brain,causing unendurable headaches.

name: Beheeyem
flavorText: It can manipulate an opponent’s memory.Apparently, it communicates by flashingits three different-colored fingers.

name: Litwick
flavorText: Litwick shines a light that absorbs thelife energy of people and Pokémon,which becomes the fuel that it burns.

name: Lampent
flavorText: This ominous Pokémon is feared.Through cities it wanders, searchingfor the spirits of the fallen.

name: Chandelure
flavorText: It absorbs a spirit, which it then burns.By waving the flames on its arms,it puts its foes into a hypnotic trance.

name: Axew
flavorText: They use their tusks to crush theberries they eat. Repeated regrowthmakes their tusks strong and sharp.

name: Fraxure
flavorText: Since a broken tusk will not grow back,they diligently sharpen their tusks onriver rocks after they’ve been fighting.

name: Haxorus
flavorText: They are kind but can be relentlesswhen defending territory. They challengefoes with tusks that can cut steel.

name: Cubchoo
flavorText: When it is not feeling well, its mucusgets watery and the power of itsIce-type moves decreases.

name: Beartic
flavorText: It can make its breath freeze at will.Very able in the water, it swims aroundin northern seas and catches prey.

name: Cryogonal
flavorText: When its body temperature goes up, itturns into steam and vanishes. When itstemperature lowers, it returns to ice.

name: Shelmet
flavorText: When attacked, it defends itself byclosing the lid of its shell. It can spita sticky, poisonous liquid.

name: Accelgor
flavorText: When its body dries out, it weakens.So, to prevent dehydration, it wrapsitself in many layers of thin membrane.

name: Stunfisk
flavorText: Its skin is very hard, so it is unhurteven if stepped on by sumo wrestlers.It smiles when transmitting electricity.

name: Mienfoo
flavorText: In fights, they dominate with onslaughtsof flowing, continuous attacks. Withtheir sharp claws, they cut enemies.

name: Mienshao
flavorText: It wields the fur on its arms like a whip.Its arm attacks come with such rapiditythat they cannot even be seen.

name: Druddigon
flavorText: It warms its body by absorbing sunlightwith its wings. When its body temperaturefalls, it can no longer move.

name: Golett
flavorText: The energy that burns inside itenables it to move, but no one has yetbeen able to identify this energy.

name: Golurk
flavorText: It flies across the sky at Mach speeds.Removing the seal on its chest makesits internal energy go out of control.

name: Pawniard
flavorText: Blades comprise this Pokémon’s entirebody. If battling dulls the blades, itsharpens them on stones by the river.

name: Bisharp
flavorText: It leads a group of Pawniard.It battles to become the boss, but willbe driven from the group if it loses.

name: Bouffalant
flavorText: Their fluffy fur absorbs damage,even if they strike foes with afierce headbutt.

name: Rufflet
flavorText: They crush berries with their talons. They bravelystand up to any opponent, no matter how strongit is.

name: Braviary
flavorText: They fight for their friends without anythought about danger to themselves.One can carry a car while flying.

name: Vullaby
flavorText: Their wings are too tiny to allow them to fly.They guard their posteriors with bones that weregathered by Mandibuzz.

name: Mandibuzz
flavorText: It makes a nest out of bones it finds.It grabs weakened prey in its talonsand hauls it to its nest of bones.

name: Heatmor
flavorText: It breathes through a hole in its tailwhile it burns with an internal fire.Durant is its prey.

name: Durant
flavorText: They attack in groups, coveringthemselves in steel armor toprotect themselves from Heatmor.

name: Deino
flavorText: It tends to bite everything, and itis not a picky eater. Approaching itcarelessly is dangerous.

name: Zweilous
flavorText: After it has eaten up all the food in its territory,it moves to another area. Its two heads do notget along.

name: Hydreigon
flavorText: This brutal Pokémon travels the skies onits six wings. Anything that moves seemslike a foe to it, triggering its attack.

name: Larvesta
flavorText: This Pokémon was believed to havebeen born from the sun. When it evolves,its entire body is engulfed in flames.

name: Volcarona
flavorText: When volcanic ash darkened theatmosphere, it is said that Volcarona’sfire provided a replacement for the sun.

name: Cobalion
flavorText: This legendary Pokémon battled againsthumans to protect Pokémon.Its personality is calm and composed.

name: Terrakion
flavorText: This Pokémon came to the defense ofPokémon that had lost their homes ina war among humans.

name: Virizion
flavorText: This Pokémon fought humans in orderto protect its friends. Legends about itcontinue to be passed down.

name: Tornadus-incarnate
flavorText: The lower half of its body is wrapped ina cloud of energy. It zooms throughthe sky at 200 mph.

name: Thundurus-incarnate
flavorText: Countless charred remains mar thelandscape of places through whichThundurus has passed.

name: Reshiram
flavorText: This Pokémon appears in legends.It sends flames into the air from itstail, burning up everything around it.

name: Zekrom
flavorText: Concealing itself in lightning clouds,it flies throughout the Unova region.It creates electricity in its tail.

name: Landorus-incarnate
flavorText: Lands visited by Landorus grant suchbountiful crops that it has been hailedas “The Guardian of the Fields.”

name: Kyurem
flavorText: It generates a powerful, freezingenergy inside itself, but its body becamefrozen when the energy leaked out.

name: Keldeo-ordinary
flavorText: By blasting water from its hooves, it canglide across water. It excels at usingleg moves while battling.

name: Meloetta-aria
flavorText: Its melodies are sung with a special vocalizationmethod that can control the feelings of those whohear it.

name: Genesect
flavorText: Over 300 million years ago, it was fearedas the strongest of hunters.It has been modified by Team Plasma.
